## Data format

The CSV file must have these columns:

| Column | Description |
|---|---|
| `Date and Time` | Timestamp (e.g. `01/02/2023 17:05`) |
| `Open` | Opening price of the minute |
| `High` | Highest price of the minute |
| `Low` | Lowest price of the minute |
| `Close` | Closing price of the minute |
| `VWAP` | Volume weighted average price |
| `Volume` | Number of contracts traded |
| `Up Ticks` | Number of up-tick trades |
| `Down Ticks` | Number of down-tick trades |
| `Same Ticks` | Number of same-price trades |

